00:03:44.169 --> 00:03:47.973
who had been following the
Russo-Japanese War in Manchuria

00:03:47.973 --> 00:03:51.310
and had seen kind of the
evolution of trenches,

00:03:51.310 --> 00:03:55.990
nobody predicted that kind of
war.

00:03:55.990 --> 00:03:58.378
I'll talk about military
strategy at the end today,

00:03:58.378 --> 00:04:01.449
or--in the plans for the
war--or,

00:04:01.449 --> 00:04:03.819
depending on time,
the timing,

00:04:03.819 --> 00:04:07.258
